These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
Beverage: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
Transport: boat, snowmobile, quad-bike, scooter
1. Beverage:hot-chocolate is between Beverage:cola and Transport:snowmobile##2
2. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left or right of Transport:boat##3
3. Beverage:hot-chocolate is somewhere between Beverage:tea and Beverage:cola##7
4. Transport:snowmobile is in an even position##4
5. Beverage:tea is on the right of Transport:quad-bike##1
6. Transport:snowmobile is somewhere to the left of Transport:boat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| Transport      | quad-bike  | snowmobile | scooter        | boat |

